Each household within this zone, which includes about 275 properties, would be eligible for two guest placards and could request up to ten passes for a single special event each year. 

The police department, with town manager approval, would reserve the right to temporarily suspend the no parking restrictions for large community events like the annual Beach to Beacon race.

